description:
So what is new in mobile? Google just had Google I/O, Apple just had WWDC, there's been announcements left right and centre!

Come find out what's changed and what features are available to developers now/soon.

The lineup will include:

• Jack Newcombe - What's new in iOS

• Andrew Wyld - What's new in Android

• Alex West - What's new in Windows Mobile

location.address: Broad Quay House, Broad Quay, Bristol, BS1 4DJ
location.name: JUSTEAT Technology

title: SWMobile: What's new in mobile
